Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.82,0:00:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to end up like this too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll end up living on dragonflies\Nand flies for the rest of your life too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn me into a frog or whatever!\NI'm not saying anything more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even underlings have pride.\NI'm a ninja too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I have to say to an outsider\N who knows nothing about our nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Still a ninja\Neven if an underling, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm not too keen about\Ninterrogation either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk is over. However, you're going\Nto stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go ask this god of yours in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya! What's the big idea,\Nsummoning me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's about the key to Naruto's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. It's not about training.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my reasons, but I thought of\Nreleasing you for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Release me? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to fight\Na pretty tough opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So tough that you needed to release me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I wish to press\Nthe storage release seal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How long until you return?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it'll take too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if anything happens to me,\Ngo store yourself inside Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The key that corresponds to Naruto's\N Eight-Signed Seal is transcribed on my belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Each year,\Nthe Fourth Hokage's seal weakens!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The key remains in order to re-seal it\Nwhen it becomes necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To place such a key right next\Nto the safe is unheard of!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Minato entrusted it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was always meant to be\Nreturned to Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you talked me into loosening\Nthe Tetragram Seal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't forgotten\Nwhat the results were, have you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the fact that Minato left me\Nthe jutsu for the key convinces me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that he intended for Naruto\Nto perfect that jutsu one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That jutsu? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:02:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Naruto even require such a jutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He would never be able to\Ncontrol the Nine-Tails' chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When that key was loosened,\NNaruto's own chakra was thrust aside
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and a large amount of\Nthe Nine-Tails' chakra leaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nine-Tails nearly\Ntook control of Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If the seal weakens any further
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Nine-Tails completely\Novertakes Naruto,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be totally against\Nthe will of the Fourth Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Minato used the Reaper Death Seal only\Non the Nine-Tails' yin chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He purposely split the Nine-Tails' power\Ninto yin and yang,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and sealed the yang power into Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to leave\Nthe Nine-Tails' chakra to Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Minato go so far as sealing\N the Nine-Tails' chakra into his own son?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? Maybe it just turned out\Nthat way by coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps, as a parent, he wanted\Nto pass on the power to his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know because I was Minato's teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He never did anything without\Ngood reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Minato must have known\Nsomething important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And he entrusted the Nine-Tails' power\Nto his own son because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're reading too much into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nine-Tailed Fox Demon that\Nattacked the Hidden Leaf Village long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is said to have been a natural disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, I've begun to suspect\Nthat it wasn't a natural phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It may have been manually summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! It has always been known that the Nine-Tails\N is a natural disaster that mysteriously appears
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,whenever humanity becomes\Nsteeped in evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, there is no one in this world powerful\N enough to summon the likes of the Nine-Tails!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the thing.\NThere {\i1}was{\i0} one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:04:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The founder of the Uchiha Clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Madara Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! Madara Uchiha lived during the era\N when the Hidden Leaf Village was established!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have been alive\Nfifteen, sixteen years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And everyone knows that the First Hokage\N defeated Madara Uchiha at the Final Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So your theory is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just have this feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that fills me with unease.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You return to the Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get there, see Ibiki.\NHe already knows you're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, I hope this works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:21.52,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(751.875,585)}The Man Who Became God\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Jiraiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Jiraiya Sensei, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How nostalgic...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll you do, Pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not on our side, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll kill him.\NIt's far too late for regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I came forth in this body in order\Nto kill the intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain... I'll handle him until you arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style! Flame Bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Toad Subjugation...\NArt of the Manipulated Shadow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping to lure out a fellow named Pain,\N but little did I expect you to take the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've honed your jutsu magnificently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But even more,\Nyou've become quite a catch, Konan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you had died...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, you turned into\Na flimsy sheet of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're his messenger...\NThe Lady Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, Konan,\N you're the messenger for this so-called god?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is an intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You should kill him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Move away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is Pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And that makes you an angel...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Does putting on an act like that\Nhave its benefits?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have received orders from our god.\NI will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toad Oil Bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't spread your wings\Nwith all that oil, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to love origami,\N and you were the kindest among the three kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What became of the other two?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagato...and Yahiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard they had died.\NWere they just rumors too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...\NSo this Pain is one of them, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your purpose?\N Appearing before us after all these years...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you all hadn't been part\Nof the Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you had died.\NI never expected this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you're thinking you should've done what that Orochimaru suggested back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shall I kill these children?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've seen many war orphans.\N{\i1}It's pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They would be better off {\i1}if we just\N put them {\i1}out of their misery right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved us instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too late now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We've embraced his ideology\Nand made our move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't regret letting you live at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm so disappointed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I taught you ninjutsu to enable you\Nto live through those harsh times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You were all, without a doubt,\Nmy students.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:13:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The world may still be a cruel place,\Nbut to attack me without a greeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,For a few years after that time,\NI heard your names mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You had made a reputation for yourselves in a few confrontations,\N but I heard later that you had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know nothing about what happened\Nto us afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't. But why the Akatsuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What the Akatsuki is doing is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the decision I've made...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You look very different.\NBut those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That shape... That ripple pattern...\N{\i1}I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Rinnegan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:14:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were Pain... Nagato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you've strayed off\Nthe path of good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to know.\NAfter all, you are an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You've changed, Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Summoning Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Foam! Leave it to my student\N{\i1}to know my weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He intends to wash away the oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Konan, stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Art of the Raging Lion's Mane!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagato... I want to ask you a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Yahiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...\NThere was such a guy, wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He died a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagato... You...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to protect those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter what kind of pain\N{\i1}I have to endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?\NThe old you wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Too many people die here.\NThat pain made me grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a stupid, foolish kid will grow up\Nwhen he learns what pain is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing pain controls one's words\Nand thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But abandoning one's love for a friend...\N Is that what it means to become an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei... You are still just a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,However, through this never-ending pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have matured and become\Neven more than a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... From a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.47,0:16:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When one becomes a god,\Nyour words and thoughts become absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, since you are human
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it can't be helped\Nif you don't understand what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you become that twisted?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Things I couldn't see when I was human\Nare clear to me now that I am a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And being a god,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize that there are things\NI can do which man cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To put it simply, evolving beyond man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to put an end to\Nthis senseless, war-torn world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a god's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If that is your purpose,\Nwhy are you gathering Tailed Beasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You are going to die anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So I shall tell you the true purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will use the Sealed Tailed Beasts...\Nto develop a new Forbidden Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With just one such jutsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a large nation can be\Ndestroyed instantaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be the most powerful,\Nthe ultimate Forbidden Jutsu weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How will making such a thing\Nend the fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't it simply intensify the conflicts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There are disputes\Nthroughout the nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you put a quick end\Nto them all, Jiraiya Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my question to you!\NAnswer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You give each warring nation\Na Forbidden Jutsu weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they possess such a power,\Nthey are bound to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tens of millions will die instantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and people will become scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,People...and nations will learn\Nwhat pain is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That fear will breed a strong aversion\Nto war and the fighting will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be said that this world is still\N in the process of growing and stabilizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain will make the world mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In the same way that I matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In order for the world to grow up\Nand become wiser
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a god's hand is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach the world pain in order to\Nmake it grow up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you believe that is your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...because I am the god of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten good\Nat telling jokes...Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Joke? I'm not joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My ideal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you're next summoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, you are a small existence\Nwhich never matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Summoning Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A kid treating me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm no longer human either!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,These tears of blood,\Noverflowing with rage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I went from the Sannin to Sage!\NThe Monstrous Toad of Mount Myoboku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Master Jiraiya...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't matured at all...\NYou're just as clumsy as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mister Gamaken!\NDon't jostle around during my juncture!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of clumsy...
